properties.description: Detour #12: Marathon (miles 19, 20, 21) and Half Marathon (miles 6 + 7): West of Mandela Parkway in West Oakland From 9:00am to 1:30pm: Take a right on Wood Street northbound, right on 34th Street, stay on 34th and cross San Pablo, left on Martin Luther King, Jr Way, take sharp right at 47th Street onto Highway 24 westbound toward I-580 or I-980. After 1:30pm: Runners will have cleared area; streets will be reopened to normal traffic.
